import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom';
import NavigationBar from './NavigationBar'; // Import the navigation bar component
import JournalingPage from './JournalingPage'; // This would be the component for your journaling page
import DataFetcher from './DataFetcher'; // Ensure this path is correct
import './app.css'; // This is fine as long as app.css is in the same directory as index.js

ReactDOM.render(
    <Router>
    <NavigationBar />
    <Switch>
      <Route path="/" exact component={DataFetcher} />
      <Route path="/journaling" component={JournalingPage} />
    </Switch>
    </Router>,
  <React.StrictMode>
    <DataFetcher />
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById('root')
);
